<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 00:57:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>朝鲜金正恩在普京访问会谈中夸耀与俄罗斯“无敌”关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-koreas-kim-boasts-invincible-ties-with-russia-amid-talks-putin-visit-2024-06-12/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周三称，朝鲜领导人金正恩在致俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的信息中表示，朝鲜与俄罗斯是“无敌的战友”，外界猜测普京即将访问朝鲜。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 00:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/north-koreas-kim-boasts-invincible-ties-with-russia-amid-talks-putin-visit-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>据 NHK 报道，日本考虑制裁包括中国在内的帮助俄罗斯乌克兰战争的公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-considers-sanctioning-firms-including-chinese-aiding-russias-ukraine-war-2024-06-12/</link><description>据公共广播公司 NHK 周三报道，日本正在考虑对包括中国公司在内的公司实施制裁，这些公司通过提供莫斯科军方可以使用的材料来支持俄罗斯对乌克兰的战争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 00:14:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-considers-sanctioning-firms-including-chinese-aiding-russias-ukraine-war-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>尽管金价接近历史最高纪录，但淘金热仍席卷亚洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-rush-grips-asia-despite-near-record-prices-2024-06-11/</link><description>行业官员表示，尽管金价徘徊在 5 月份创下的纪录高位附近，但亚洲黄金需求仍在飙升，因为买家抢购黄金以对冲地缘政治和经济不确定性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 23:32:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-rush-grips-asia-despite-near-record-prices-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>两名美国男子因串谋向中国出售伊朗石油而入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/two-us-men-jailed-conspiracy-sell-iranian-oil-china-2024-06-11/</link><description>美国司法部表示，两名得克萨斯州男子于 11 月被美国陪审团定罪，罪名是试图违反华盛顿实施的制裁，试图出售伊朗石油，并串谋洗钱，并于周二被判处 45 个月监禁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 23:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/two-us-men-jailed-conspiracy-sell-iranian-oil-china-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：中国CPI领先于美国CPI，美联储双重打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-11/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 21:48:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国特使警告匈牙利，与中国的密切关系“附带条件”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-warns-hungary-that-close-ties-with-china-come-with-strings-attached-2024-06-11/</link><description>美国驻布达佩斯特使周二严厉批评匈牙利政府与中国密切的政治和商业关系，这种关系往往“附带条件，而且往往以主权为代价”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 19:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-warns-hungary-that-close-ties-with-china-come-with-strings-attached-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社报道，美国考虑对中国获取人工智能芯片施加更多限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-weighs-more-limits-chinas-access-ai-chips-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-06-11/</link><description>彭博新闻社周二援引知情人士的话报道称，拜登政府正在考虑进一步限制中国获得用于人工智能的芯片技术。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 16:20:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-weighs-more-limits-chinas-access-ai-chips-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>尽管韩国队失利，中国队仍保有世界杯预选赛的希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/chinese-keep-world-cup-qualifying-hopes-alive-despite-korea-defeat-2024-06-11/</link><description>周二，中国队在首尔以0比1不敌韩国队，但仍以微弱优势晋级2026年世界杯亚洲区预选赛第三轮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:52:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/chinese-keep-world-cup-qualifying-hopes-alive-despite-korea-defeat-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰情报机构称中国网络间谍活动范围超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/dutch-intelligence-says-chinese-cyber-espionage-goes-wider-than-it-suspected-2024-06-11/</link><description>荷兰军事情报部门周一表示，中国的网络间谍活动比其最初想象的更为广泛，其目标是西方政府和国防公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:43:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/dutch-intelligence-says-chinese-cyber-espionage-goes-wider-than-it-suspected-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国因维吾尔劳工而禁止从中国进口鞋类、海鲜、铝业公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-bars-imports-footwear-seafood-aluminum-firms-over-uyghur-labor-2024-06-11/</link><description>根据美国政府周二在网上发布的通知，美国又将三家公司列入禁止从涉嫌在中国强迫维吾尔人劳动的公司进口产品的名单。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 14:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-bars-imports-footwear-seafood-aluminum-firms-over-uyghur-labor-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>世界银行表示全球经济增长趋于稳定，但低于新冠疫情前的水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-market-data/world-bank-says-global-growth-stabilizing-well-below-pre-pandemic-levels-2024-06-11/</link><description>世界银行周二表示，美国经济强于预期的表现促使其小幅上调2024年全球增长前景，但警告称，到2026年，总体产出仍将远低于疫情前的水平。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 13:43:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-market-data/world-bank-says-global-growth-stabilizing-well-below-pre-pandemic-levels-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>行业组织表示，尽管电动汽车关税调查，中国汽车制造商仍致力于欧洲市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-committed-europe-despite-ev-tariff-probe-industry-group-says-2024-06-11/</link><description>中国一家领先的汽车工业协会周二表示，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车进行反补贴调查不会影响中国汽车制造商在欧洲的投资计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 11:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-committed-europe-despite-ev-tariff-probe-industry-group-says-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>随着西方制裁加剧，中国敦促金砖国家发挥更大作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-greater-brics-role-western-sanctions-mount-2024-06-11/</link><description>外交部长王毅周二表示，在西方对中国实施制裁和贸易限制之后，中国敦促金砖国家集团承担更大责任，树立对世界的包容性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 10:50:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-greater-brics-role-western-sanctions-mount-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：苹果的人工智能推动以及欧洲的麻烦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-11/</link><description>阿曼达·库珀 (Amanda Cooper) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 10:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>越南总统希望妥善处理与中国的海上争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-president-wants-maritime-disputes-with-china-be-well-managed-2024-06-11/</link><description>越南国家主席苏林周二向中国驻河内大使熊波表示，妥善处理海事争端并尊重各国利益非常重要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-president-wants-maritime-disputes-with-china-be-well-managed-2024-06-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>